info.author: Barthelemy Dagenais
info.description:
ghmiles is a Python library that generates a milestone model from the issues in
a GitHub repository. ghmiles can optionaly generate an HTML page similar to a
`Trac roadmap`_. 

A milestone is a list of issues having the same label. The progress of a
milestone is obtained by dividing the number of closed issues by the number of
total issues. 

Users of ghmiles can specify which labels identify a milestone by providing a
regular expression. 

.. _`Trac roadmap`: http://trac.edgewall.org/roadmap

info.html_description:
ghmiles is a Python library that generates a milestone model from the issues in a GitHub repository. ghmiles can optionaly generate an HTML page similar to a Trac roadmap.

A milestone is a list of issues having the same label. The progress of a milestone is obtained by dividing the number of closed issues by the number of total issues.

Users of ghmiles can specify which labels identify a milestone by providing a regular expression.
